# Local dev secrets for `npx wrangler dev`.
# Copy this file to .dev.vars (which is gitignored) and fill in the secret.
#
# YNAB_CLIENT_ID lives in wrangler.jsonc (it's not secret — it appears in
# every browser's OAuth redirect URL anyway). If you fork, override it
# there for local dev too.
#
# In production, YNAB_CLIENT_SECRET goes in the Cloudflare dashboard as
# a Secret under Workers > ynab-spending-dashboard > Settings >
# Variables and Secrets. Never commit the real value to git.

YNAB_CLIENT_SECRET=
